  (str content) (str `1
THE AGRICULTURAL AND PROCESSED FOOD PRODUCTS EXPORT DEVELOPMENT
AUTHORITY ACT, 1985
_________
ARRANGEMENT OF SECTIONS
________
CHAPTER I
P RELIMINARY
S ECTIONS
1. Short title, extent and commencement.
2. Definitions.
3. Power to amend Schedule.
CHAPTER II
A GRICULTURAL AND P ROCESSED F OOD P RODUCTS E XPORT D EVELOPMENT A UTHORITY
